    "description": "Stuck/Hung Job incident on the Store Sales pipeline (RTL_STS_STUCK): marketing campaign-attribution join hangs on a cartesian product.",
    "symptoms": "The daily attribution join task has been running 8 hours against a 40-minute baseline, consuming escalating Snowflake credits.",
    "root_cause": "A join key (campaign_id) became non-unique in the source Ad Platform export after a schema change introduced duplicate rows per campaign per creative variant, turning a 1:1 join into an unbounded fan-out.",
    "business_impact": "Marketing attribution dashboard unavailable ahead of a scheduled budget-reallocation meeting; Snowflake compute costs for the account spike unexpectedly.",
    "resolution": "Kill the query, add a DISTINCT/dedup step on the source extract, add a row-count sanity-check gate before the join executes."
  },
